Package com.example.luckydragon.Controllers

Class AddEventController

java.lang.Object
com.example.luckydragon.Controllers.Controller
com.example.luckydragon.Controllers.AddEventController
public class AddEventController extends Controller
This class is a controller for the AddEventDialogFragment. Handles extracting user input for the event and updating the Event model.
